------------------------------------------------
Cloud Stream
------------------------------------------------
Bindable Channels (MessageSource...)
- Source    OUTPUT (MessageChannel)
- Processor INPUT,OUTPUT (extends Source, Sink)
- Sink      INPUT (SubscribableChannel)

